title: KOSPI 보합권, KOSDAQ 0.22% 상승
originSummary: KOSPI remained stable at the 2480 level, while KOSDAQ increased by 0.22%.

title: [코인 시황] 비트코인, 하루 새 35K서 38K 부근으로 '껑충'
originSummary: 이 기사는 연방준비제도(Federal Reserve)의 양적 조절(QT)에 대한 경고와 우려에 대해 논의합니다.
양적 조절은 연방준비제도가 금융 시장에서 자산을 판매하여 돈의 공급을 줄이는 것을 의미합니다.
이러한 조치가 경제에 미칠 수 있는 잠재적인 영향에 대한 우려가 제기되고 있습니다.

title: 뉴욕증시, PPI 하락에 모두 상승…다우 0.5%↑ ()
originSummary: The New York Stock Exchange (NYSE) rose following the release of declining producer price index (PPI) and consumer price index (CPI).
The Dow Jones Industrial Average reached its highest level since August 16th, and the S&P500 and Nasdaq indexes also experienced gains.

The decrease in PPI indicates a slowdown in inflation, which is positively impacting the market and generating expectations of an end to the Federal Reserve's rate hike cycle. Meanwhile, international markets saw varied results, with the price of West Texas Intermediate (WTI) crude oil decreasing and European markets like the CAC40 and DAX30 seeing increases.

title: 서울 아파트 가격 상승률 0.21%로 지속적인 상승세.
originSummary: According to a report, apartment prices in Seoul increased by 0.21% in the first week of November, continuing the overall trend of rising prices.
The rate of increase in apartment prices in Seoul has been slowing down for the third consecutive week.

Specific neighborhoods in Seoul, such as Dongdaemun, Yongsan, Yeongdeungpo, and Yangcheon, saw the highest increase in prices. Nationally, apartment rental prices increased by 0.12%, while Seoul saw a larger increase of 0.21% compared to the previous week.
